### Enhancements

* Ability to set a default conda environment at launch, so when you open an Anaconda Prompt, or enter `conda activate` at the command line, it will activate your preferred environment rather than `base`. 
* The command to set the default conda environment is `conda config --set default_start_environment my-favourite-env`.
* If you don't set a default start environment, `conda activate` will continue to activate `base`.

